Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.assetowner.properties

Class SemanticAssignmentProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.assetowner.properties.RelationshipProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.assetowner.properties.SemanticAssignmentProperties
public class SemanticAssignmentProperties extends RelationshipProperties
SemanticAssignmentProperties links an element to a glossary term to indicate that the glossary term describes its meaning.
